query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q tq s) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('judaism')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('blessing',
'halacha',
'history',
'minhag',
'parshanut-torah-comment',
'shabbat',
'sources-mekorot',
'tefilla');
